                292.5,
                2127.5
            ],
            "ignore": false,
            "order": 10,
            "anno_id": 1,
            "text": "After applying previous steps to all history conversations  $H$ , we will finally obtain a history memory matrix  $C \\in \\mathbb{R}^{M \\times d}$  containing a history memory for each history conversation, where  $M$  is the number of history conversation sessions.",
            "line_with_spans": [
                {
